let me fast toward a little
bit and get right to it.

00:24:15.060 --> 00:24:16.820
But some of these maps show you.

00:24:16.820 --> 00:24:21.070
So Southeast Asia
is graduating from

00:24:21.070 --> 00:24:24.751
this post-colonial geography
of 10 different countries

00:24:24.751 --> 00:24:27.250
into one that, again, is densely
infrastructurally connected

00:24:27.250 --> 00:24:29.230
the way that Europe is.

