00:32:27.300 --> 00:32:30.310
So this is, I know, a mission
that a lot of key technology

00:32:30.310 --> 00:32:32.650
companies play.

00:32:32.650 --> 00:32:35.290
And having traveled
around and looked so much

00:32:35.290 --> 00:32:37.860
at the catalytic impact
that connectivity has,

00:32:37.860 --> 00:32:39.660
whether it's energy,
transportation,

00:32:39.660 --> 00:32:42.040
or communications,
I strongly believe

00:32:42.040 --> 00:32:44.450
in that connectivity mission.

